      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear 333 hp. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. Mechanical provenance is documented with preventative rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe carrier panel. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec bushings and a flawless undercarriage free of oxidation. This is a mechanically superlative example for the discerning collector who demands peak atmospheric performance and structural integrity.",
