      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in showroom-fresh condition that must be seen to be fully appreciated. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, free from any swirls, rock chips, or door dings, having been meticulously garage-kept under a soft cover since day one. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats are supple and show zero signs of bolster wear, while the original floor mats look untouched. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system, functions exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history detailing preventative maintenance performed well ahead of schedule. There are absolutely no leaks, no rattles, and the engine delivers smooth, effortless power. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that bridges the gap between a used car and a brand-new vehicle.",
